          <div class="text-lg" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; color: #F8F7F4; font-weight: 400;">Master Suite Retreat</div>
          <div class="text-xs mt-1" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: rgba(248,247,244,0.55); font-weight: 300;">Warangal, Telangana</div>
